Output images/log.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set Theme "TokyoNight"
Set Padding 24

Hide
Type "source ~/.zshrc && bash ~/Desktop/repos/agent-changelog/tapes/reset-session.sh gif-log && clear && openclaw tui --session gif-log"
Enter
Sleep 30s
Show

Type "/agent-changelog log --detail"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Hide
Sleep 30s
Show
Sleep 3s
